our_solution_title: This is a rare window of opportunity
our_solution_subtitle1: Quantum computing is not an incremental technology. It is the kind of step change that comes along once in a century, and that change is approaching faster than we thought possible even a few years ago.
our_solution_subtitle2: Businesses that become early adopters during this window will have an immediate advantage when it comes time to turn this technology into commercial value.
our_solution_subtitle3: Quantum is your partner in getting ready. We have the expertise, educational tools, and unmatched quantum technology to help you chart your path to quantum value in your industry.
our_solution_subtitle4: Global businesses are readying themselves today for the era of quantum computing

cloud_service_description: Easily and efficiently define workloads with new, optimized primitive programs that perform foundational quantum computing functions. Input circuits to Sampler to output an error-mitigated readout of quasiprobabilities and identify your most relevant solutions. Estimator efficiently calculates and interprets expectation values of quantum operators required for many algorithms.

about_us_title: Quantum computing all over the world
about_us_description: We are committed to fostering a truly global quantum economy. Our iconic Quantum System One is already in strategic partner locations in Germany and Japan, with more on the way in the United States, South Korea, and Quebec, Canada. With our strategic partners, we aim to build national quantum ecosystems, develop workforces, and accelerate R&D on a national and global scale.
